title: Sakray 0911 - Ragnarok Online
description:
This is the full Sakray 0911 setup for the MMORPG Ragnarok Online. 

In addition to Sakray you will need Raglite (or kRO) and a server patch to be able to play on a private server. These can be downloaded from our download server. 


The Excalibur Network has two free Ragnarok Online servers to offer:

Excalibur Chronicles 
Rates: 10x Exp, 8x Item drop

AvalonRO
Rates: 200x Exp, 100x Item drop


Please visit www.excalibur-ro.com for more information, downloads and a detailed installation guide!
